descript.abstract: Data from: American Community Survey, 5-year Series 2009-2013King County, Washington census tracts with American Community Survey data derived from the U.S. Census Bureau's demographic profiles (DP02-DP05). The geo service includes over 50 attributes of the most frequently requested data.When downloading the data, please select "GDB Download" under "Additional Resources" to preserve long field names. The associated file geodatabase contains a feature class referred to as "top 20" that includes these 50+ attributes. There are an additional four feature classes which include the data from each data profile. Data from: American Community Survey, 5-year Series 2009-2013
descript.purpose: King County, Washington census tracts with American Community Survey data.
